  <official_title>A Prospective, Single Center, Open Label, Proof of Principle Study to Assess the Efficacy and Safety of 150 Units of Botulinum Toxin-A Intra-Muscular Injection in the Prevention of Hair Loss in Men With Androgenetic Alopecia</official_title>
